reviewText: This got here a week earlier then expected, so that is nice since it is a gift. Vacuumed sealed wrapping of DVDs, so that was nice to know that it had not been opened prior to shipment.
Quick postage from U.S, next time I will check Dvd regions thou, lucky I have a dvd player that will play them.
This was a gift for my grandaughter. She was so happy to get it. I will be ordering more in the future. There are many to order. Great shows, real funny too.
